Terrible movie, but thanks for the upload!
Are there any PROPER English subtitles? I only found auto-translated crap so far.

Well these new English subs just got posted on 8/11/10:
http://www.opensubtitles.org/en/subtitles/3941708/wall-street-money-never-sleeps-en
They are not perfect, but they are much better than the Google translated subs available so far.
They work with both this rip (noir) as well as the Maxspeed version.

Here is my rate: (Out of 10)
Audio= 9
Video= 10
Movie= 9

Better than the first sequel for me.
